  "bio_raw": "Nusrat Tajkia has over two years of experience in teaching both literature and ELT courses. She did her BA(honors) and MA at Jahangirnagar University. Before starting her career as a teacher, she worked at a social enterprise. She has a Cambridge CELTA from the British Council.  She is currently teaching at the Department of English and Humanities at the University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh (ULAB).",
